      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要给这个项目做一个甘特图，标题就叫'A Gantt Diagram'。时间轴用标准的年月日格式，从2024年开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
