      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把第一个任务画出来：A task从2024-01-01开始，持续30天。第二个任务用after a1来关联，持续20天。这样第二个任务会自动从1月31日开始对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A task",
        "Another task",
        "after a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，依赖关系用after a1来建立，这样时间线就自动衔接上了。两个任务的命名和ID都确认没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "after a1",
        "a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到第二个任务没有单独起ID，这样后续如果再加任务引用它可能会不太方便。需要给'Another task'也加个ID吗，比如a2？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "暂时不用，目前就这两个任务，用after a1的依赖方式已经足够清晰了。如果后续扩展再补ID也行。",
